<p>Reports syntax errors in the Spring Expression Language (SpEL) code, such as unresolved references and invalid locations.</p>

<p><b>Example:</b></p>
<pre><code lang="java">
@Controller
public class MyController {
    @Value("#{T(java.lang.Math).<strong>unknown</strong>()}") // Cannot resolve property or method 'unknown'
    public void setValue(String s) {}
}
</code></pre>
